This repository contains binary font files which are omitted from the chezmoi source.

To install the Nerd Fonts referenced by the original dotfiles, either:

- Copy the font files manually into `~/.local/share/fonts/NerdFonts/` and run `fc-cache -f`.
- Or install fonts via your OS package manager or a dotfiles font installer.

If you want the fonts tracked in chezmoi, import them with:

  chezmoi add --source ~/.local/share/fonts/NerdFonts/<font-file>

